{"tid":2349624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 又上大陸搵人仔 賣港賊！","createTime":"2021-01-01T16:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T17:14:20.000Z","uid":305710,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05a8a114bb0ebea2ee2fe51976048ac155e5c91f","tid":2349624,"uid":305710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"大家有無諗過係邊個搞到前幾年樂壇得返啲唔唱得？<br />\n前幾年大家都會講「香港樂壇已死」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年終於有啲睇頭 有林家謙 Serrini 呢啲彈起<br />\n<br />\n但最後呢？ <br />\n<br />\n香港人都係會選擇用眼去聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n技巧 音準 全部都唔考慮 <br />\n<br />\n只係會care 靚唔靚仔<br />\n<br />\n搞成今日咁 香港人係時候唔好成日瀨中資乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n反而要諗 係邊個唔撐有料嘅本地歌手 <br />\n<br />\n令到呢堆人要走上去？<br />\n<br />\n有幾多人有比錢睇rubber? 有幾多人會買碟支持有料歌手？<br />\n<br />\n搞死香港樂壇 最大兇手咪香港人本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6080bdd91d509b1398326e119bcb851a682df2","tid":2349624,"uid":305710,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"其實古天樂都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如年年古天樂拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還掂有無料都唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824e93fca02d1e84c4c59e6e20b5a2a1ceb219cf","tid":2349624,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"成堆偽人上晒去春晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7abc5d71bc428bce554e744dbbfa9f9f1a29103","tid":2349624,"uid":305710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"香港人：90年代係輝煌時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1705f7b9385b001e7473b27f857